included.description:
I handled all of the Brokers personal clients dealings. Once they had landed on a home or had the buyer, I was completing the transaction with the lenders, title company, inspectors and clients. It was a huge opportunity for me to learn the complete back end of a Real Estate office and transactions. 
 During this time I had also taken care of a few Property Management activities. Collecting rents, posting notices, inspections, ordering repairs and interviews.
included.title: Real Estate Agent/Broker assistant

included.description:
I've had the complete pleasure of helping so many people. I worked with famous architects, artists, doctors, and CEO's. My fun energy made everything easy and seamless. Making sure your new baby was absolute spotless! I had great pride in making it easy to work wirth and buy in the heart of the busy city. 
  Clients would cross the bridge and if I was lucky enough to gather some details before they arrived. I would have 95% of the paperwork completed. So, we'd drive their new baby around the block or freeway. Walk right back in, finish up the paperwork, and 45 minutes later out burning gas. A entire transaction I could have completed in less than a hour in some cases.

included.summary:
www.Facebook.com/BioKeepR
  Positive, motivated, and always growing.  I've been serving others my entire life, from Electronics, Automotive, to Real Estate. 
 
 I am now in the process of building a media storage device and app, for people to pass on their life stories and lessons. 
 
 The app is designed to assist with creating content in an organized fashion. You're able to download content from the net or create and store your own on the external hard drive.

 The BioKeepR will comes with a extra battery, a removable hard drive, and the screen can be replaced by you. 
If it should ever break. 

 These are 3 elements not available on mobile devices today. 
  
 The App is simple enough for grandma to use. Creating and passing on their
True Legacy. 
 
 True Self is not online. Intimacy is not shared with the world, our families Deserve More. 

Not to mention cloud services don't need our important content, and internet service is not everywhere at all times.
